# Google OAuth Client ID
# 1. Ve a https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# 2. Crea un "OAuth client ID" tipo "Web application"
# 3. Agrega http://localhost:5173 como Authorized JavaScript origin
# 4. Copia el Client ID aquí:
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=tu-client-id-google.apps.googleusercontent.com
